variety of choices at a reasonable price and portion. And taste wise is not bad at all

Chicken wings at $1 only ...
The spring chicken is no joke... superbly marinated. You can taste the marinate even to the bones. Well done. Taste like Arnold's but Arnold's seemed milder compared to this. Recommend üëç
